{"id": "art-305", "label": "Art. 305", "title": "Art. 305: Începerea urmăririi penale", "slug": "art-305", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 305: Începerea urm&#259;ririi penale </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_595241600\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1951\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_595241600\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Când actul de sesizare îndepline&#351;te condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute de lege, organul de urm&#259;rire penal&#259; dispune începerea\nurm&#259;ririi penale cu privire la fapta s&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259; ori a\nc&#259;rei s&#259;vâr&#351;ire se preg&#259;te&#351;te, chiar dac&#259; autorul\neste indicat sau cunoscut.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_654643523\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1950\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_654643523\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Începerea urm&#259;ririi penale &#351;i respectiv\ncontinuarea efectu&#259;rii urm&#259;ririi penale se dispun prin\nordonan&#355;&#259; care cuprinde, dup&#259; caz, men&#355;iunile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 286 alin. (2) lit. a)-c) &#351;i g).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_366503332\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1949\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_366503332\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Atunci când exist&#259; probe din care s&#259; rezulte\nb&#259;nuiala rezonabil&#259; c&#259; o anumit&#259; persoan&#259; a\ns&#259;vâr&#351;it fapta pentru care s-a început urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;\n&#351;i nu exist&#259; vreunul dintre cazurile prev&#259;zute la art. 16 alin.\n(1), organul de urm&#259;rire penal&#259; dispune ca urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;\ns&#259; se efectueze în continuare fa&#355;&#259; de aceasta, care\ndobânde&#351;te calitatea de suspect. M&#259;sura dispus&#259; de organul de cercetare\npenal&#259; se supune, în termen de 3 zile, confirm&#259;rii procurorului care\nsupravegheaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;, organul de cercetare penal&#259;\nfiind obligat s&#259; prezinte acestuia &#351;i dosarul cauzei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1652776350\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1948\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1652776350\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Fa&#355;&#259; de persoanele pentru care urm&#259;rirea\npenal&#259; este condi&#355;ionat&#259; de ob&#355;inerea unei autoriza&#355;ii\nprealabile sau de îndeplinirea unei alte condi&#355;ii prealabile, efectuarea\nurm&#259;ririi penale se poate dispune numai dup&#259; ob&#355;inerea\nautoriza&#355;iei ori dup&#259; îndeplinirea condi&#355;iei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}